  "prompt": "Who are some of the famous alumni of NIT Puducherry?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **National Institute of Technology Puducherry (NIT Puducherry)** is a relatively young institution, officially designated as an NIT in 2019. Given its recent establishment as an NIT, it may not yet have a long list of widely recognized alumni compared to some of the older and more established NITs in India.\n\nHowever, graduates from NIT Puducherry are actively contributing to various fields such as engineering, technology, research, and entrepreneurship. Many alumni are pursuing advanced studies in prestigious institutions around the world, while others are making their mark in the industry through innovative projects and startups.\n\nIt's also worth noting that as the institute continues to grow and expand its programs, the number of notable alumni is expected to increase over time. For the most up-to-date information on distinguished alumni, you might consider visiting the official NIT Puducherry website or connecting with their alumni association.",
